name: TopDown Survival Shooter
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Top Down Survival Shooter is a cryptocurrency-based game that involves players engaging in challenging battles for survival against numerous enemies. As participants progress through the game, they earn $ Shooter tokens and accumulate a variety of weapons and equipment. The objective is to test players' ability to survive in a hostile environment.
